text.section:
The Board shall submit to the Department on or before July 1 of each year:
The name of each student who participated in the program during the preceding year;
The name of each student projected to participate in the program during the upcoming year;
The county in which each student who participated in the program during the preceding year was domiciled;
The county in which each student projected to participate in the program during the upcoming year is domiciled;
The total number of students that participated in the program during the preceding year;
The total number of students projected to participate in the program during the upcoming year;
The actual operation budget for the preceding year; and
The projected operating budget for the upcoming year.
